{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/abcs-grep-i","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"23ce8121-9ed7-5635-8d43-1a44bd9ad835","html":"<h2 id=\"i\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i\" aria-label=\"i permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I</h2>\n<p>Use the <code class=\"language-text\">-i</code> flag to ignore case​ in the results.</p>\n<p>Let’s return back to our handy <code class=\"language-text\">test.txt</code> file and add “Happy” to the end:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sad\nhappy\nawake\ncoffee\nwork\nschool\nHappy</code></pre></div>\n<p>To ignore case differences run:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ grep -i \"happy\" test.txt\nhappy \nHappy</code></pre></div>\n<p>The uppercase variant is also an “ignore” flag, but this time we are ignoring binary files.\nSo if the current directory with <code class=\"language-text\">test.txt</code>, also contained <code class=\"language-text\">test.pdf</code>, the following would ignore the pdf file:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ grep -I \"happy\" *\ntest.txt:happy</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts//posts/abcs-grep-i","tagSlugs":null},"frontmatter":{"date":"2023-11-03","description":"What does grep -[iI] do?","tags":null,"title":"The ABC's of grep - I","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts//posts/abcs-grep-i"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","2764776372","401334301","63107425"]}